query: SELECT se.*, s.fullName, s.registrationNumber, sub.name as subjectName FROM student_enrollments se JOIN students s ON se.studentId = s.id LEFT JOIN subjects sub ON se.subjectId = sub.id WHERE s.registrationNumber = '2023306650';
